To assess model accuracy, we used three separate measures. First, the percentage of deviance explained by each mean hourly air temperature model was calculated using the pseudo-determination coefficient D2 (Mateo and Hanselman 2014), using1D2=1-residualdeviance/totaldeviance\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
